    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176720/extras/198d3f0e12705c7549fa12aa0834d14c.avif?t=1772159849\" width=1560 height=793 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176720/extras/de966537b35338c949b25427b856ebf6.poster.avif?t=1772159849\" width=1170 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176720/extras/de966537b35338c949b25427b856ebf6.webm?t=1772159849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176720/extras/de966537b35338c949b25427b856ebf6.mp4?t=1772159849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Lancelot, Mother Goose, Dorothy Gale, and many more iconic characters with a modern cartoon twist!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gorgeous hand-drawn artwork brings every stage, every character, every moment of battle to life!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even the music is remixed from the ground-up from the public domain! Like our &quot;Punk-Rockabye Baby&quot;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gorgeous optional visual effects like FILM GRAIN and CEL SHADOW provide a fuzzy nostalgic feeling!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176720/extras/176df9ee568e027a5f318517aa7bd543.avif?t=1772159849\" width=1560 height=86 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176720/extras/6ddb8c753ed4f60feb79edab259db4d0.poster.avif?t=1772159849\" width=1170 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176720/extras/6ddb8c753ed4f60feb79edab259db4d0.webm?t=1772159849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176720/extras/6ddb8c753ed4f60feb79edab259db4d0.mp4?t=1772159849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LIGHT, STRONG, and SPECIAL attacks make the zany flow of combat feel straightforward, even for first time players!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Genre veterans will find depth and complexity preserved in familiar mechanics like moonwalking, foxtrotting, and more: even WAVEDASHING has an easy introduction for new players with an optional single-button command!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>CUSTOMIZABLE CONTROLS</u></strong> let anyone play with exactly the button layout you're looking for! Genre veterans can even choose from our pre-set profiles inspired by the layouts of other platform fighting greats, in order to feel right at home.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Enjoy our pre-made rulesets, or customize your own!</strong></u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>PARTY MODE</strong></u> warps out-of-bounds players across the screen instead of eliminations—no more disheartening SDs!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <u><strong>LEGAL</strong></u> rules run tournament-legal settings and bans casual stages from random selection</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>STOCK</strong></u>, <u><strong>TIME</strong></u>, <u><strong>STAMINA</strong></u>, <u><strong>TEAMS</strong></u>, even <u><strong>ITEM</strong></u> and <u><strong>RANDOM STAGE</strong></u> toggles are here!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176720/extras/176df9ee568e027a5f318517aa7bd543.avif?t=1772159849\" width=1560 height=86 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176720/extras/ddd0afab1909b5325e836e113d6422cd.poster.avif?t=1772159849\" width=1170 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176720/extras/ddd0afab1909b5325e836e113d6422cd.webm?t=1772159849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176720/extras/ddd0afab1909b5325e836e113d6422cd.mp4?t=1772159849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hone your skills and take them online with our rollback netcode, or stay home and have a party fit for Gatsby!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>ONLINE QUICKPLAY</strong></u> for fast 1v1 matches</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>PRIVATE LOBBIES</strong></u> to group with up to four friends plus spectators!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>ROLLBACK NETCODE</strong></u> makes for a smooth online experience! (Ethernet is always recommended)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy their exciting combos and hilarious interactions together in local multiplayer—or online with rollback netcode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176720/extras/176df9ee568e027a5f318517aa7bd543.avif?t=1772159849\" width=1560 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Royalty Free-For-All is coming soon! Stay tuned by wishlisting above and following our social media channels.</p>",
